@startuml
title CLARISSA Layered Responsibility Architecture

skinparam Shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

rectangle "Neuro-Symbolic Governance\nRules · Constraints · Escalation" as GOV
rectangle "LLM Reasoning & Interaction\nPlanning · Explanation · Dialogue" as LLM
rectangle "Reinforcement Learning\nAction Sequences · Skill" as RL
rectangle "Simulation Substrate\nProduction Simulators · Open/Research Simulators · CLARISSA Native Kernel" as SIM

GOV -down-> LLM : constrains
LLM -down-> RL : orchestrates
RL  -down-> SIM : acts through

note right of GOV
Sets permissions, thresholds,
approval gates, audit rules.
end note

note right of RL
Learns skill from consequences,
not authority or physics laws.
end note

@enduml
